[Bu kararın etkileri — pozitif ve negatif]
```

## Monolith vs Microservices Karar Agaci
```
├── Takim kac kisi? < 5 -> Modular Monolith
├── Bagimsiz deploy gerekli mi? -> Microservices
├── Farkli olcekleme ihtiyaci? -> Microservices
├── Baslangiç mi? -> Modular Monolith (sonra parcala)
├── Karmasik domain + cok takim? -> Microservices
└── Basit CRUD? -> Monolith yeterli

VARSAYILAN: Modular Monolith ile basla
├── Her modul kendi Bounded Context'i
├── Moduller arasi: internal event (MediatR notification)
├── Hazir olunca: modul -> service extract et
```

## Bounded Context Mapping
```
Her domain modulu icin:
├── Context Adi
├── Core Entity'ler
├── Sorumluluk Alani
├── Diger Context'lerle Iliski:
│   ├── Partnership (esit isbirligi)
│   ├── Customer-Supplier (talep-temin)
│   ├── Conformist (olduğu gibi kabul)
│   └── Anti-Corruption Layer (ceviri katmani)
```

## API Kontrat Tasarimi
```yaml
# docs/agents/contracts/create-order.yaml
endpoint: POST /api/v1/orders
summary: Yeni siparis olustur
authentication: Bearer JWT
permissions: ["order:create"]

request:
  body:
    customerId: { type: string, format: uuid, required: true }
    items:
      type: array
      minItems: 1
      items:
        productId: { type: string, format: uuid, required: true }
        quantity: { type: integer, minimum: 1, required: true }
    notes: { type: string, maxLength: 500, required: false }

responses:
  201:
    body:
      isSuccess: true
      data:
        id: { type: string, format: uuid }
        orderNumber: { type: string }
        status: "Draft"
    headers:
      Location: "/api/v1/orders/{id}"
  400:
    body:
      type: "validation-error"
      title: "Validation Failed"
      errors: [{ property: "items", message: "..." }]
  401: { description: "Token gecersiz" }
  403: { description: "Yetki yok" }
  409: { description: "Duplicate order" }
```

## API Versioning Strategy
```
v1 -> v2 gecis:
1. Yeni endpoint: /api/v2/orders (eski de calismaya devam)
2. Deprecation header: Sunset: 2026-06-01
3. Migration guide dokumante et
4. 3 ay transition period
5. v1 kaldir

KURAL: Breaking change = yeni version. Non-breaking = ayni version.
```

## Consistency Model Karar Agaci
```
├── Ayni servis icinde? -> Strong consistency (DB transaction)
├── Farkli servisler arasi? -> Eventual consistency
│   ├── Saga pattern (orchestration veya choreography)
│   ├── Outbox pattern (event publish + DB transaction)
│   └── Idempotent consumer (duplicate event handling)
├── Read consistency kritik? -> CQRS + read model (eventual)
└── Financial/critical? -> 2PC (son care, kacinilmali)
```

## Caching Strategy
```
Karar Agaci:
├── Sik okunan, nadir degisen? -> Cache (Redis)
│   ├── TTL: 5-30 dk (use case'e gore)
│   ├── Invalidation: event-driven (entity degistiginde)
│   └── Key: tenant:{tid}:{type}:{id}
├── Her zaman guncel olmali? -> No cache, direct DB
├── Session/user bazli? -> Distributed cache (Redis)
└── Static/config? -> Memory cache (IMemoryCache)
```

## Technology Selection Framework
```
Her teknoloji secimi icin degerlendir:
├── Maturity: Production-ready mi? (GA, community buyuklugu)
├── Ecosystem: .NET entegrasyonu var mi?
├── Performance: Benchmark'lar nedir?
├── Learning Curve: Takim ogrenme suresi?
├── License: Ticari kullanimda sorun var mi?
├── Support: Long-term support var mi?
├── Community: Stack Overflow, GitHub star, activity?
└── Alternative: Daha basit bir cozum var mi?
```

## Distributed Systems Fallacies
```
1. Ag guvenilirdir -> Retry + circuit breaker
2. Latency sifirdir -> Timeout + async
3. Bandwidth sinirsizdir -> Pagination + compression
4. Ag guvenlidir -> mTLS + encryption
5. Topoloji degismez -> Service discovery
6. Tek admin vardir -> GitOps + IaC
7. Transport maliyeti sifirdir -> Batch + gRPC
8. Ag homojendir -> Protocol abstraction
```

## Architecture Fitness Functions
```
Otomatik olcum (CI'da):
├── Dependency: Katman ihlali = 0 (NetArchTest)
├── Complexity: Cognitive complexity < 15
├── Coupling: Circular dependency = 0
├── Size: Class < 300 LOC, Method < 30 LOC
├── Coverage: Domain+App > %90
├── Performance: API P95 < 500ms
├── Security: Vulnerable dependency = 0
```

## Anti-Pattern'ler
| Anti-Pattern | Dogru Yaklasim |
|---|---|
| Distributed monolith | True Bounded Context + async communication |
| Shared database across services | DB per service / schema per module |
| Synchronous chain (A->B->C->D) | Async events + saga |
| Technology hype | Boring technology principle |
| No ADR | Her onemli karar ADR ile |
| Premature optimization | Measure first, optimize second |
